{"tid":1069740,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日lunch幫老細整電腦 竟然比我發現左一個秘密","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T08:35:37.000Z","uid":8655,"like":151,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"301582818a99eb6a2f110569dc50d68a9bda5137","tid":1069740,"uid":8655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"我係公司it部既 今日收到call話老細部電腦壞左 <br />\n咁我打算趁lunch時間快快手整埋就出去嘆個靚燒雞<br />\n<br />\n點知整整下突然有人開門 我即刻9秒9哩左入個file櫃度<br />\n我都唔知點解我要咁驚 一開門竟然係老細帶埋佢秘書入黎<br />\n老細刪埋門 然後坐埋位笑騎騎咁 個女秘書就自動波除佢條褲<br />\n<br />\n屌等我仲有d冧呢條女 原來又係臭雞 突然有個男同事開門沖入黎 老細褲都著唔切 坐係度聽佢講 好似話唔知咩飯盒啊微波爐咁 屌呢d都唔重要啦 老細三兩句打發左佢走<br />\n依家同個女秘書大戰緊 睇到我扯到恆曬 lunchtime就黎完 <br />\n啱啱拍左片<br />\n片就唔share啦 大家覺得我應唔應該威脅個秘書好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好 反正都係臭雞 屌到佢反皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好 其實佢都應該係比老細迫良為娼"},{"pid":"cbb93d1803ce721b000ce96a7e3e15f13a1f9414","tid":1069740,"uid":62822,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b8061100d9a934d3b2c0419540e598a68034f3f","tid":1069740,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"樓主收收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c5bd8d62a40c8d641d1306451f015ba4cc3a0e","tid":1069740,"uid":187072,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"冇片，你都係走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89176a95740ce5382718989f64ae18b29740e36d","tid":1069740,"uid":104678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:17:56.000Z","msg":"純文字討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e8c6206a2f49606b5099276b0260800532b90c","tid":1069740,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"又撚<img src=\"/assets/fac